structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 343, sec. 10, effective July 13, 1990. -- Created 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 371, sec. 3, effective January 1, 1981.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Tax on motor vehicles and trailers to be used in determining maximum permissible county revenue.
